title: Part B
stimulusHtml:
2 points maximum

Determination (1 point)

· Exercise does not affect prolactin release

Justification (1 point)

· The T=1 hour with-exercise mean and the T=1 hour without-exercise mean are within ±2S E X ¯ MathType@MTEF@5@5@@3B61@ .

· The ±2S E X ¯ MathType@MTEF@5@5@@3B61@ error bars for the T=1 hour with-exercise time point and the T=1 hour time without-exercise point overlap.

· The ±2S E X ¯ MathType@MTEF@5@5@@3B61@ error bars for the T=0 and T=1 hour with-exercise time points overlap.

· The T=0 hour with-exercise mean and the T=1 hour with exercise-mean are within ±2S E X ¯ MathType@MTEF@5@5@@3B61@ .
